<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hi, <%= @user.first_name %></h1>
    <p>
        We’re thrilled to have you as a new user. You’re one step closer to meeting cool people who 
      love the same awesome things as you. After you’ve clicked the confirmation link, we’ll ask you 
      to input a few interests in each category. Don’t worry about adding all of them right away. You can always add or remove interests by going to your profile and clicking “add interests.”
    </p>
    <p>
      Click  <%= link_to 'here', ('www.cliqwith.me' + activate_path(id: @user.id, code: @user.activation)) %> to activate your account.<br> 
    </p>
    <p>
      This is an automatically generated email, so please don’t reply to it. If you are having trouble activating your account, write to us at support@cliqwith.me so we can help you out.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>

    <p>-Cliq</p>
  </body>
</html>